OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with variable amounts of
OL,7,Fcloud and some late brightness in
OL,8,Fplaces. Then cloudy overnight with
OL,9,Fsome patchy rain and drizzle.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FPatchy light rain at first,
OL,12,Fotherwise it will be dry. Starting off
OL,13,Fcloudy but some bright spells in
OL,14,Fplaces by afternoon. Warm in any
OL,15,Fsunshine.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,18,Fmainly dry few days with variable
OL,19,Famounts of cloud and some spells of
OL,20,Fsunshine. Perhaps some heavy showers
OL,21,Flate Friday. Very warm or hot.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
